# <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b4/Flag_of_Turkey.svg" alt="Turkey" height="32px" width="auto"> PostCSS Turkish Stylesheets

> [PostCSS](https://github.com/postcss/postcss) plugin for writing Turkish Style Sheets.


## Installation

```console
$ npm install --save-dev postcss-turkish-stylesheets
```

## Example

### Input

```css
.error-msg {
    görünüm: blok;
    sol-kenar: 3px düz kırmızı;
    font-büyüklüğü: 15px;
    satır-genişliği: 20px;
    arkaplan: saydam;
    renk: kırmızı !önemli;
}
```

### Output

```css
.error-msg {
    display: block;
    border-left: 3px solid red;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 20px;
    background: transparent;
    color: red !important;
}
```

## Usage

### Gulp

```js
var gulp = require('gulp');
var rename = require('gulp-rename');
var postcss = require('gulp-postcss');
var autoprefixer = require('autoprefixer')
var trCSS = require('postcss-turkish-stylesheets');

gulp.task('default', function () {
    var processors = [
        trCSS()
    ];

    return gulp.src('src/**/*.css')
        .pipe(postcss(processors))
        .pipe(rename('output.css'))
        .pipe(gulp.dest('build'));
});
```

